name: tbl2asn

variants.name: build_system
variants.description: Build systems supported by the package

description:
Tbl2asn is a command-line program that automates the creation of
sequence records for submission to GenBank.

dependencies.name: libidn
dependencies.description:
GNU Libidn is a fully documented implementation of the Stringprep,
Punycode and IDNA 2003 specifications. Libidn's purpose is to encode and
decode internationalized domain names.

dependent_to.name: prokka
dependent_to.description:
Prokka is a software tool to annotate bacterial, archaeal and viral
genomes quickly and produce standards-compliant output files.
